ine%20banks%20have%20lower%20overhead%20costs%20and%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20high%20rates%20to%20attract%20new%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHigh-Yield%20Savings%20Accounts%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20high-yield%20savings%20accounts%20provide%20the%20security%20of%20a%20savings%20account%20with%20the%20added%20bonus%20of%20a%20high%20APY.%20Savings%20accounts%20are%20held%20at%20a%20bank%20or%20credit%20union%20%E2%80%94%20not%20invested%20through%20a%20brokerage%20account%20%E2%80%94%20and%20are%20best%20for%20saving%20cash%20in%20pursuit%20of%20shorter-term%20goals%2C%20like%20a%20vacation%20or%20big%20purchase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHigh-Yield%20Checking%20Accounts%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20high-yield%20checking%20accounts%20tend%20to%20pay%20slightly%20lower%20rates%20than%20high-yield%20savings%2C%20but%20even%20they%20are%20strong%20in%20today's%20rate%20environment.%20A%20checking%20account%20is%20like%20a%20hub%20for%20your%20money%3A%20If%20your%20paycheck%20is%20direct%20deposited%2C%20it's%20typically%20to%20a%20checking%20account.%20If%20you%20transfer%20money%20to%20pay%20a%20bill%2C%20you%20typically%20do%20it%20from%20a%20checking%20account.%20Checking%20accounts%20are%20used%20for%20everyday%20spending%20and%20usually%20come%20with%20checks%20and%2For%20debit%20cards%20to%20make%20that%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EMoney%20Market%20Accounts%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-money-market-accounts%5C%22%3Ebest%20money%20market%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20be%20considered%20a%20middle%20ground%20between%20checking%20and%20savings%3A%20They%20are%20used%20for%20saving%20money%20but%20typically%20provide%20easy%20access%20to%20your%20account%20through%20checks%20or%20a%20debit%20card.%20They%20usually%20offer%20a%20tiered%20interest%20rate%20depending%20on%20your%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ECash%20Management%20Accounts%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%