o%20face%20challenges%20early%20on%20in%20their%20career%2C%20but%20Gen%20Zers%20feel%20they're%20discriminated%20against%20%E2%80%94%20largely%20because%20of%20their%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20have%20a%20point.%20In%20a%20survey%20from%20Resume%20Builder%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20over%20a%20third%20(36%25)%20of%20the%201%2C000%20hiring%20managers%20polled%20said%20they%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiring-managers-biased-against-gen-z-older-workers-survey-says-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20bias%20against%20Gen%20Z%20candidates%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20research%20from%20Applied%2C%20an%20inclusivity%20and%20diversity-led%20recruitment%20software%2C%20also%20found%20that%20out%20of%202%2C000%20respondents%20in%20the%20UK%2C%2036%25%20of%20Zoomer%20respondents%20believe%20they%20have%20experienced%20hiring%20bias.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20results%2C%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20email%2C%20showed%20that%20Gen%20Z%20respondents%20felt%20the%20top%20reason%20for%20this%20discrimination%20was%20their%20age%20%E2%80%94%2021%25%20of%20respondents%20aged%2016-24%20cited%20this.%20Age%20came%20above%20ethnicity%20(19%25)%20and%20gender%20(15%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22da53d663-333f-40f2-a0b6-ccaa0e3eacfa%5C%22%3EAI%20and%20outdated%20methods%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKhyati%20Sundaram%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Applied%2C%20told%20BI%20there%20could%20be%20a%20couple%20of%20reasons%20behind%20this%20prejudice%20against%20Zoomers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20developments%20in%20AI%20have%20made%20recruiters%20%26quot%3Bhypervigilant%2C%26quot%3B%20Sundaram%20said.%20Gen%20Zers%20are%20seen%20as%20the%20cohort%20most%20likely%20to%20write%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20and%20cover%20letters%20with%20the%20help%20of%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20AI%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20seeing%20more%20and%20more%20call%20mediocre%20applications%20or%20applications%20that