0herself%20an%20Olympic%20medal%20in%20the%20women's%2066kg%20category%20in%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20woman%20from%20her%20country%20to%20achieve%20this%20milestone.%20Khelif's%20victory%20over%20Hungary's%20Anna%20Luca%20Hamori%20has%20not%20only%20secured%20Algeria's%20first%20boxing%20medal%20since%202000%20but%20has%20also%20secured%20her%20place%20into%20the%20semi-finals%2C%20where%20she%20will%20face%20Thailand's%20Janjaem%20Suwannapheng%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Algerian%20has%20found%20herself%20at%20the%20center%20of%20a%20gender%20eligibility%20debate.%20Alongside%20Taiwanese%20boxer%20Lin%20Yu-ting%2C%20Khelif%20has%20faced%20scrutiny%20and%20online%20abuse%20due%20to%20differing%20eligibility%20criteria%20set%20by%20the%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20(IOC)%20and%20the%20International%20Boxing%20Association%20(IBA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20athletes%20were%20disqualified%20from%20last%20year's%20World%20Championships%20by%20the%20IBA%20following%20unspecified%20eligibility%20tests%20but%20were%20cleared%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20under%20IOC%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20send%20a%20message%20to%20all%20the%20people%20of%20the%20world%20to%20uphold%20the%20Olympic%20principles%20and%20the%20Olympic%20Charter%2C%20to%20refrain%20from%20bullying%20all%20athletes%2C%20because%20this%20has%20effects%2C%20massive%20effects%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20SNTV%20in%20Arabic.%20%26quot%3BIt%20can%20destroy%20people%2C%20it%20can%20kill%20people's%20thoughts%2C%20spirit%2C%20and%20mind.%20It%20can%20divide%20people.%20And%20because%20of%20that%2C%20I%20ask%20them%20to%20refrain%20from%20bullying.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20in%20contact%20with%20my%20family%20two%20days%20a%20week.%20I%20hope%20that%20they%20weren't%20affected%20deeply.%20They%20are%20worried%20about%20me.%20God%20willing%2C%20this%20crisis%20will%20culminate%20in%20a%20gold%20medal%2C%20and%20that%20would%20be%20the%20best%20response%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhelif%20expressed%20her%20hope%20that%20her%20journey%20would%20culminate%20in%20a%20gold%20medal.%20She%20also%20thanked%20the%20IOC%20and%20its%20president%2C%20Thomas%20Bach%2C%20for%20their%20support%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20the%20Olympic%20Committee%20has%20done%20me%20justice%2C%20and%20I%20am%20happy%20with%20this%20remedy%20because%20it%20shows%20the%20truth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Lin%20Yu-ting%2C%20who%20will%20compete%20against%20Turkey's%20Esra%20Yildiz%20in%20the%20women's%2057kg%20semifinal%2C%20has%20also%20been%20embroiled%20in%20the%20controversy.%20Following%20her%20unanimous%20decision%20victory%20over%20Bulgaria's%20Svetlana%20Kamenova%20Staneva%2C%20Lin%20has%20faced%20a%20mix%20of%20support%20and%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20official%20decision%20was%20announced%2C%20Staneva%20made%20a%20double%20XX%20gesture%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20female%20chromosome%2C%20and%20initially%20appeared%20to%20snub%20Lin.%20However%2C%20after%20the%20referee%20declared%20Lin%20the%20winner%2C%20Staneva%20opened%20the%20ropes%20for%20Lin%2C%20acknowledging%20her%20opponent's%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELin%2C%2028%2C%20has%20remained%20focused%20and%20grateful%20for%20the%20support%20from%20her%20country.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20all%20of%20Taiwan's%20people%20are%20standing%20behind%20me%20and%20supporting%20me%2C%20and%20I%20will%20carry%20this%20energy%20to%20the%20end.%20Even%20though%20I%20won%20this%20match%2C%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20I%20can%20relax%3B%20I%20still%20need%20to%20work%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20after%20victory%20over%20Svetlana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Taiwan%20Olympic%20Committee%20released%20a%20statement%20reaffirming%20Lin's%20eligibility%20to%20compete%2C%20as%20determined%20by%20the%20IOC's%20rules.%20The%20committee%20condemned%20the%20online%20abuse%20directed%20at%20Li