rporate%20giants%20stared%20down%20at%20massive%20losses.%20The%20US%20markets%20fell%20over%202.43%25%20on%20Friday%20while%20the%20Asian%20peers%20added%20to%20their%20losses%20as%20they%20opened%20after%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20Indian%20indexes%20were%20trading%203%25%20in%20the%20red%20at%20their%20lowest%20on%20Monday.%20Sensex%20had%20slipped%20below%20the%2080%2C000-level%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20about%20four%20weeks%20-%20marking%20the%20worst%20fall%20since%20the%20share%20markets%20tumbled%20over%204%2C300%20points%20on%20June%204%2C%20the%20election%20results%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20massive%20drop%20that%20erased%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20investor%20wealth%20worldwide%20came%20after%20the%20US%20jobs%20data%20fanned%20fears%20of%20a%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20labour%20market%20data%2C%20which%20came%20after%20the%20Indian%20market%20hours%20but%20just%20in%20time%20before%20the%20US%20closing%2C%20showed%20the%20world's%20biggest%20economy%20added%20just%20114%2C000%20jobs%20last%20month%20-%20below%20the%20June%20figures%20and%20much%20lower%20than%20expected.%20The%20jobless%20rate%20in%20the%20US%20had%20risen%20to%20its%20highest%20level%20since%20October%202021%2C%20it%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20boosted%20bets%20on%20several%20Federal%20Reserve%20interest%20rate%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%20said%20they%20have%20increased%20their%2012-month%20recession%20odds%20by%2010%20percentage%20points.%20%26quot%3BThe%20premise%20of%20our%20forecast%20is%20that%20job%20growth%20will%20recover%20in%20August%20and%20the%20FOMC%20will%20judge%2025bp%20cuts%20a%20sufficient%20response%20to%20any%20downside%20risks.%20If%20we%20are%20wrong%20and%20the%20August%20employment%20report%20is%20as%20weak%20as%20the%20July%20report%2C%20then%20a%2050bp%20cut%20would%20be%20likely%20in%20September%2C%26quot%3B%20Reuters%20cited%20them%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20jobs%20data%20erased%20the%20gains%20from%20the%20lacklustre%20factory%20data%20that%20had%20come%20a%20day%20before%20and%20sparked%20losses%20in%20the%20US%20markets.%20Tech%20heavyweights%20like%20Amazon%20and%20Microsoft%20took%20the%20brunt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20aggravated%20the%20situation%20was%20the%20simmering%20tensions%20between%20Iran%20and%20Israel%20that%20has%20already%20given%20hints%20of%20a%20full-blown%20war.%20The%20escalation%20came%20after%20a%20top%20Hamas%20leader%20was%20assassinated%20when%20he%20was%20in%20Tehran%20to%20attend%20a%20government%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAxios%2C%20an%20American%20news%20website%2C%20has%20cited%20a%20warning%20from%20top%20diplomat%20Antony%20Blinken%20that%20Iran%20could%20launch%20an%20attack%20on%20Israel%20as%20early%20as%20today.%20There%20were%20reports%20Israel%20could%20also%20sanction%20a%20preemptive%20strike%20on%20Iran%20to%20prevent%20any%20attack%20on%20their%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Asian%20markets%2C%20back%20from%20the%20weekend%2C%20woke%20up%20with%20Monday%20blues.%20Tokyo%20led%20the%20collapse%20with%20Nikkei%20plunging%20over%2012%25%2C%20its%20worse%20since%202011%2C%20while%20Seoul%20and%20Taipai%20tanked%20over%208%25%20each.%20Singapore%20shed%20nearly%205%25%20and%20Sydney%20fell%20more%20than%203%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20equity%20market%20too%20opened%20in%20the%20red%20this%20morning%20with%20Sensex%20falling%202%2C600%20points%20at%20one%20point%20and%20Nifty%20shedding%20over%20700%20points.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20markets%20will%20open%20this%20evening%20after%20the%20weekend%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722844440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fcu3of3po_share-market-generic-markets-fall-markets-generic-shares-generic-stocks-generic-reuters_625x300_05_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fexplained-what-led-to-global-equities-bloodbath-6266762%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20global%20sell-off%20has%20led%20to%20a%20major%20bloodbath%20in%20the%20equity%20markets%20as%20corporate%20giants%20stared%20down%20at%20massive%20losses.%20The%20US%20markets%20fell%20over%202.43%25%20on%20Friday%20while%20the%20Asian%20peers%20added%20to%20their%20losses%20as%20they%20opened%20after%20the%20weekend.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fexplained-what-led-to-global-equities-bloodbath-6266762%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fexplained-what-led-to-global-equities-bloodbath-6266762%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fexplained-what-led-to-global-equities-bloodbath-6266762%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Loud%20DJ%20Music%20Blamed%20For%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Wall%20Crash%20That%20Killed%209%20Children%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20wall%20collapse%20incident%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Sagar%20district%2C%20which%20left%20nine%20children%20dead%2C%20may%20have%20been%20caused%20by%20loud%20music%2C%20according%20to%20local%20residents.%20The%20children%2C%20in%20the%208%20to%2015%20years%20age%20group%2C%20were%20sitting%20next%20to%20a%20dilapidated%20house's%20wall%20during%20a%20religious%20ceremony%20in%20the%20adjoining%20Hardaul%20Baba%20temple%20when%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOwned%20by%20Mulu%20Patel%2C%20the%20dilapidated%20house%20is%20about%2050%20years%20old%20and%20was%20precariously%20supported%20by%20bamboo%20beams.%20Around%209%20am%20yesterday%2C%20loud%20music%20from%20a%20DJ%20set-up%20started%20playing%20in%20the%20temple.%20On%20the%20itinerary%20of%20the%20religious%20event%20was%20Bhagwat%20Katha%20and%20making%20small%20clay%20shivlings.%20The%20children%20were%20doing%20this%20when%20the%20wall%2C%20already%20run%20down