20levels%20are%20often%20higher%20than%20145%20decibels.%20This%20creates%20intense%20vibrations.%20For%20an%20average%20person%2C%20an%20exposure%20to%20sound%20levels%20above%2055%20decibels%20for%20more%20than%20five%20minutes%20can%20be%20harmful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoud%20music%20at%20religious%20places%20has%20been%20a%20key%20focus%20area%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20ever%20since%20Mr%20Yadav%20took%20over%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20last%20year.%20He%20had%20earlier%20banned%20use%20of%20loudspeakers%20above%20permitted%20decibel%20levels.%20This%20crackdown%20was%20later%20extended%20to%20DJ%20systems%20too%2C%20frequently%20used%20at%20religious%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20also%20directed%20officers%20to%20identify%20dilapidated%20buildings%20across%20the%20state%20and%20take%20action%20so%20that%20such%20incidents%20don't%20recur.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722844380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fc8p8ujjg_sagar-collapse_625x300_05_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-wall-collapse-mohan-yadav-loud-music-caused-wall-collapse-that-killed-9-children-locals-blame-dj-set-6266763%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20wall%20collapse%20incident%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Sagar%20district%2C%20which%20left%20nine%20children%20dead%2C%20may%20have%20been%20caused%20by%20loud%20music.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-wall-collapse-mohan-yadav-loud-music-caused-wall-collapse-that-killed-9-children-locals-blame-dj-set-6266763%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-wall-collapse-mohan-yadav-loud-music-caused-wall-collapse-that-killed-9-children-locals-blame-dj-set-6266763%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3