ral%20significance.%20But%2C%20to%20Nabam%2C%20the%20end%20did%20not%20justify%20the%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20ensure%20that%20traditions%20continue%20without%20disrupting%20the%20ecosystem%2C%20Nabam%20started%20Arunachal%20Ivory%20and%20Ornaments%20in%202022%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20Likha%20Nana%20(29)%2C%20a%20post-graduate%20in%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftribes-6-1722420329.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nabam%20Bapu%20and%20his%20wife%20Likha%20Nana%20were%20troubled%20by%20how%20innocent%20animals%20were%20harmed%20in%20order%20to%20continue%20tribal%20traditions.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftribes-6-1722420329.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftribes-6-1722420329-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftribes-6-1722420329-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftribes-6-1722420329-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftribes-6-1722420329-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359186%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENabam%20Bapu%20and%20his%20wife%20Likha%20Nana%20were%20troubled%20by%20how%20innocent%20animals%20were%20harmed%20in%20order%20to%20continue%20tribal%20traditions%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Nabam%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeading%20a%20revolution%20in%20the%20Northeast%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20(Likha%20and%20I)%20were%20always%20keen%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%