%20accessories%20made%20using%20animal%20hide%20and%20teeth%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Nabam%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20glance%20at%20the%20traditional%20%3Cem%3EPar%20Eij%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EPomo%3C%2Fem%3E%20attire%20donned%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Nyishi%20community%20will%20reveal%20that%20it%20is%20beautiful.%20But%20a%20closer%20look%20will%20reveal%20the%20things%20that%20make%20up%20its%20beauty%20%E2%80%94%20a%20bundle%20of%20animal%20parts%20interspersed%20with%20coloured%20fabrics%20and%20accessories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20start%20at%20the%20top.%20An%20eagle-clawed%20hairstyle%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20striking%20features%20of%20the%20Nyishi%20tribe%E2%80%99s%20dress.%20%E2%80%9CReal%20eagle%20claws%20are%20used%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nabam%20points%20out.%20You%20will%20also%20observe%20the%20headgear%2C%20%3Cem%3EByopa%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Econsisting%20of%20a%20cane%20helmet%20adorned%20with%20the%20beak%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F53080%2F6-bird-saving-communities-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGreat%20Indian%20Hornbill%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%E2%80%98vulnerable%E2%80%99%20species%20according%20to%20the%20IUCN%20(International%20Union%20for%20Conservation%20of%20Nature).%20Nabam%20explains%20that%20wearing%20the%20beak%20signifies%20beauty%20and%20youthfulness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftribes-2-1722419872.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20beak%20of%20the%20Great%20Indian%20Hornbill%20is%20worn%20on%20the%20head%20to%20show%20beauty%20and%20youthfulness.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftribes-2-1722419872.jpg%201200w%2C%20http