hnology%2Ftech-news%2Fapple-to-launch-m4-powered-macbook-pro-imac-mini-later-this-year-report-124080500350_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fapple-to-launch-m4-powered-macbook-pro-imac-mini-later-this-year-report-124080500350_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fapple-to-launch-m4-powered-macbook-pro-imac-mini-later-this-year-report-124080500350_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Can%20India%20Create%208%20Million%20Jobs%20A%20Year%3F%20Here's%20What%20The%20Numbers%20Indicate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fjgka7oc8_jobs_625x300_05_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Budget%202024%20has%20placed%20significant%20emphasis%20on%20job%20creation%20and%20skill%20development%20to%20capitalise%20on%20the%20country's%20demographic%20advantage.%20Growing%20unemployment%2C%20political%20observers%20aver%2C%20emerged%20as%20a%20major%20concern%20during%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20needs%20to%20create%208%20million%20new%20jobs%20annually%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Economic%20Survey%2C%20to%20absorb%20into%20the%20workforce%20the%20youth%20graduating%20from%20colleges.%20And%20the%20challenge%20lies%20in%20creating%20enough%20jobs%20not%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20quantity%20but%20also%20in%20terms%20of%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20ongoing%20debate%20and%20comparisons%20regarding%20the%20jobs%20being%20created%20during%20the%20NDA%20regime%20as%20against%20those%20that%20were%20created%20during%20the%20UPA%20rule%2C%20as%20well%20as%20about%20the%20true%20unemployment%20rate%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Shares%20Across%20Agriculture%2C%20Industry%20And%20Services%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20according%20to%20a%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20report%2C%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20in%20India%20was%203.2%25%20in%20FY%202022-23%2C%20the%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%20(CMIE)%2C%20a%20private%20body%2C%20pegs%20it%20at%207.6%25.%20The%20RBI%20report%2C%20titled%20%3Cem%3EMeasuring%20Productivity%20at%20the%20Industrial%20Level%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20states%20that%20the%20total%20workforce%20in%20India%20was%20643.3%20million%20in%20FY24%2C%20with%2047%20million%20jobs%20created%20during%20the%20year.%20Approximately%20265%20million%20people%20are%20employed%20in%20agriculture%2C%20154%20million%20in%20industry%2C%20and%20219%20million%20in%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20FY23%2C%20the%20total%20workforce%20was%20596.7%20million%2C%20with%2042.4%25%20employed%20in%20agriculture%20-%20which%20puts%20the%20non-agricultural%20workforce%20at%20343.7%20million.%20Of%20the%2074%20million%20income%20tax%20returns%20filed%20in%20FY23%2C%2051.6%20million%2C%20that%20is%2C%2070%25%20of%20the%20total%2C%20were%20zero-income%20tax%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgricultural%20income%20is%20tax-exempt%2C%20so%20it%20is%20expected%20that%2042.4%25%20of%20the%20workforce%20in%20this%20sector%20would%20not%20pay%20taxes.%20However%2C%20the%20fact%20that%2070%25%20of%20total%20returns%20are%20zero-income%20returns%20indicates%20that%20there%20are%20low-paying%20jobs%20even%20in%20the%20industry%20and%20service%20sectors.%20Of%20the%20347%20million%20people%20employed%20in%20industry%20and%20services%2C%20only%2022.4%20million%20are%20paying%20taxes.%20Meaning%20that%20just%206.5%25%20of%20the%20non-agricultural%20workforce%20is%20contributing%20to%20India's%20income%20tax%20collection.%20This%20raises%20serious%20concerns%20about%20job%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20indicate%20that%20only%20around%20118%20million%20people%20in%20India%20are%20employed%20in%20salaried%20jobs%2C%20with%20just%2020%25%20earning%20more%20than%20Rs.%2050%2C000%20in%20a%20month%3B%20most%20of%20them%20have%20monthly%20salaries%20of%20less%20than%20Rs.%2020%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJobs%20Under%20NDA%20vs%20Jobs%20Under%20UPA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDecadal%20employment%20data%20from%20the%20RBI%20shows%20that%20India%20created%20125%20million%20jobs%20during%20FY14-23%20(that%20is%2C%20during%20the%20NDA%20regime)%2C%20compared%20to%20the%2029%20million%20created%20in%20FY04-14%20(the%20UPA%20regime).%20Even%20if%20we%20exclude%20agriculture%2C%20job%20creation%20in%20manufacturing%20and%20services%20amounted%20to%2089%20million%20during%20the%20NDA%20regime%20versus%2066%20million%20during%20the%20UPA%20dispensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20in%20FY04-14%2C%20the%20agricultural%20workforce%20declined%20by%2037%20million%2C%20while%20industry%20and%20services%20each%20saw%20an%20increase%20of%2033%20million.%20This%20indicates%20a%20strategic%20shift%20from%20agriculture%20to%20industry%20and%20services%2C%20aligning%20with%20India's%20long-term%20goal.%20Agriculture%20employs%20close%20to%2040%25%20of%20the%20workforce%20but%20contributes%20only%2015%25%20to%20the%20country's%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20FY14%20to%20FY23%2C%2036%20million%20jobs%20were%20created%20in%20agriculture%2C%2032%20million%20in%20industry%2C%20and%2057%20million%20in%20the%20service%20sector%2C%20totalling%20125%20million%20jobs%20over%20nine%20years%20on%20a%20net%20basis.%20The%20shift%20from%20agriculture%20to%20industry%20and%20services%20appears%20to%20have%20slowed%20down%20during%20this%20decade%2C%20possibly%20due%20to%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%20Many%20workers%20from%20cities%20and%20metros%20returned%20to%20their%20villages%20and%20did%20not%20come%20back%2C%20taking%20up%20agriculture-related%20jobs%20in%20their%20local%20areas%20instead.%20This%20could%20have%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20agricultural%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Promising%20Are%20The%20Recent%20Schemes%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20set%20an%20ambitious%20target%20of%20creating%20an%20additional%2041%20million%20jobs%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years%20through%20the%20schemes%20announced%20in%20the%20Budget.%20This%20target%20includes%2029%20million%20jobs%20from%20Employment-Linked%20Incentive%20(ELI)%20schemes%2C%2010%20million%20from%20internships%2C%20and%202%20million%20from%20ITI%20(Industrial%20training%20institutes)%20programmes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20enhance%20employability%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20also%20launched%20a%20scheme%20offering%20internship%20opportunities%20to%2010%20million%20youths%20in%20India's%20top%20500%20companies%20over%20five%20years.%20This%20translates%20to%204%2C000%20interns%20per%20year%20for%20each%20of%20these%20companies%2C%20totalling%202%20million%20interns%20annually.%20An%20internship%20allowance%20of%20Rs%205%2C000%20per%20month%20will%20be%20provided%20to%20youth%2C%20while%20companies%20will%20cover%20the%20cost%20of%20training%20through%20CSR%20funds.%20EaseMyTrip%20has%20already%20announced%20plans%20to%20hire%20through%20this%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20doubts%20remain%20about%20the%20feasibility%20of%20the%20scheme.%20Was%20the%20industry%20consulted%20before%20launching%20the%20ambitious%20initiative%3F%20The%20Finance%20Minister%20also%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20a%20leading%20news%20organisation%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20internship%20scheme%20was%20not%20%26quot%3Bcompulsory%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20nudging%20the%20industry%20to%20adopt%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorporate%20Sector%20Needs%20To%20Step%20Up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Economic%20Survey%20has%20subtly%20suggested%20that%20the%20corporate%20sector%20needs%20to%20contribute%20more%20to%20employment%20generation.%20It%20noted%20that%20the%20sector%20was%20%26quot%3Bswimming%20in%20excess%20profits%26quot%3B%2C%20with%20Profit%20Before%C2%A0%20Tax%20(PBT)%20nearly%20quadrupling%20between%20FY20%20and%20FY23%20and%20the%20corporate%20profits-to-GDP%20ratio%20reaching%20a%2015-year%20high%20in%20FY24.%20Yet%2C%20the%20survey%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bhiring%20and%20compensation%20growth%20hardly%20kept%20up%20with%20this%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmployment%20data%20from%20the%20top%20585%20publicly%20traded%20companies%20show%20that%20they%20collectively%20employ%207.3%20million%20people.%20How%2C%20then%2C%20can%20they%20absorb%2010%20million%20interns%3F%20For%20India%20to%20benefit%20from%20its%20demographic%20dividend%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20generate%20productive%20employment%20for%207-8%20million%20youths%20who%20will%20join%20the%20labour%20force%20each%20year.%20If%20not%2C%20this%20dividend%20could%20be%20lost.%20Can%20the%20budget%20push%20to%20achieve%20these%20job%20creation%20goals%3F%20We%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20to%20see%20the%20implementation%20of%20recently%20announced%20schemes%20in%20months%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722840300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fjlgd9vso_jobs_625x300_05_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcan-india-create-8-million-jobs-a-year-heres-what-the-numbers-indicate-6266288%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20India%20to%20benefit%20from%20its%20demographic%20dividend%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20generate%20productive%20employment%20for%207-8%20million%20youths%20who%20will%20join%20the%20labour%20force%20each%20year.%20If%20not%2C%20this%20dividend%20could%20be%20lost.%20Can%20the%20budget%20push%20to%20achieve%20these%20job%20creation%20goa%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcan-india-create-8-million-jobs-a-year-heres-what-the-numbers-indicate-6266288%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcan-india-create-8-million-jobs-a-year-heres-what-the-numbers-indicate-6266288%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcan-india-create-8-million-jobs-a-year-heres-what-the-numbers-indicate-6266288%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iran%20'doesn't%20want'%20Middle%20East%20war%20but%20Israel%20'must%20be%20punished'%20as%20families%20of%20UK%20embassy%20staff%20withdrawn%20from%20Lebanon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722840120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F08%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-hamas-gaza-israel_6647075.jpg%3F20240804132157%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Firan-doesnt-want-middle-east-war-but-israel-must-be-punished-as-families-of-uk-embassy-staff-withdrawn-from-lebanon-13191130%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iran%20has%20said%20it%20is%20not%20seeking%20to%20escalate%20the%20conflict%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20but%20its%20arch-enemy%20Israel%20must%20be%20%26quot%3Bpunished%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20country's%20foreign%20ministry%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Firan-doesnt-want-middle-east-war-but-israel-must-be-punished-as-families-of-uk-embassy-staff-withdrawn-from-lebanon-13191130%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Firan-doesnt-want-middle-east-war-but-israel-must-be-punished-as-families-of-uk-embassy-staff-withd