0in%20the%20matter%20last%20year.%20The%20Supreme%20Court's%20website%20earlier%20said%20Justice%20Narasimha%20will%20be%20pronouncing%20the%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Narasimha%20said%20Section%203(3)(b)%20of%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Corporation%20Act%20lays%20down%20that%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20can%20nominate%2010%20persons%20not%20less%20than%2025%20years%20of%20age%20and%20with%20special%20knowledge%20or%20experience%20in%20municipal%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20incorrect%20to%20suggest%20that%20power%20in%20Delhi%20LG%20was%20a%20semantic%20lottery.%20It%20is%20law%20made%20by%20the%20Parliament%2C%20it%20satisfies%20the%20discretion%20exercised%20by%20LG%20since%20law%20requires%20him%20to%20do%20so%20and%20falls%20under%20the%20exception%20of%20Article%20239.%20It%20was%201993%20DMC%20Act%20which%20first%20vested%20the%20power%20to%20nominate%20on%20LG%20and%20it%20is%20not%20a%20relic%20of%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20also%20said%20that%20a%20five-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20earlier%20ruled%20that%20Parliament%20can%20legislate%20on%20state%20and%20concurrent%20lists%20of%20Delhi.%20%26quot%3BAs%20Parliament%20has%20conferred%20power%20on%20LG%20to%20nominate%2010%20aldermen%2C%20AAP%20government%20cannot%20quarrel%20with%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20has%20250%20elected%20and%2010%20nominated%20members.%20Currently%2C%20the%20ruling%20AAP%20controls%20it%20after%20winning%20134%20seats%20in%20the%202022%20polls.%20The%20BJP%20holds%20104%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20said%20last%20year%20that%20giving%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20the%20power%20to%20nominate%20aldermen%20to%20MCD%20will%20mean%20he%20can%20destabilise%20an%20elected%20civic%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20counsel%2C%20had%20contended%20that%20the%20state%20government%20has%20been%20given%20no%20separate%20powers%20to%20nominate%20people%20to%20MCD.%20A%20practice%20of%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20nominating%20aldermen%20on%20the%20aid%20and%20advice%20of%20the%20city%20government%20has%20been%20followed%20for%20three%20decades%20now%2C%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20Sanjay%20Jain%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor's%20office%2C%20had%20argued%20that%20just%20because%20a%20practice%20has%20been%20followed%20for%2030%20years%20does%20not%20mean%20it%20is%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20has%20described%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bjolt%20to%20democracy%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20going%20to%20bypass%20an%20elected%20government%20and%20give%20all%20powers%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20so%20that%20he%20runs%20Delhi%20using%20a%20stick.%20This%20is%20not%20right%20for%20democracy.%20We%20respectfully%20disagree%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling.%20The%20verdict%20is%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20bench's%20observations%20during%20the%20hearing%2C%26quot%3B%20party%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20has%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20party%20will%20decide%20on%20the%20next%20step%20after%20going%20through%20the%20judgment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Arvind%20Kejriwal-led%20AAP%20government%20in%20Delhi%20has%20for%20long%20argued%20that%20the%20Centre%20maintains%20a%20stranglehold%20on%20the%20national%20capital%20through%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20and%20the%20elected%20city%20government%20does%20not%20have%20powers%20to%20execute%20its%20duties%20properly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MP%20Praveen%20Khandelwal%20has%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20appointed%20aldermen%20as%20per%20the%20law.%20%26quot%3BAam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%20a%20habit%20of%20making%20allegations%20on%20every%20issue.%20Their%20politics%20has%20been%20rejected%20by%20the%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722838020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F8nom5n9g_vk-saxena-arvind-kejriwal_625x300_04_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-governor-does-not-need-delhi-governments-advice-to-nominate-mcd-aldermen-rules-supreme-court-6265771%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20big%20setback%20for%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20government%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20ruled%20that%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20can%20nominate%20aldermen%20in%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD)%20without%20Delhi%20government's%20aid%20and%20advice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-governor-does-not-need-delhi-governments-advice-to-nominate-mcd-aldermen-rules-supreme-court-6265771%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-governor-does-not-need-delhi-governments-advice-to-nominate-mcd-aldermen-rules-supreme-court-6265771%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-governor-does-not-need-delhi-governments-advice-to-nominate-mcd-aldermen-rules-supreme-court-6265771%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bad%20Newz%20earns%20Rs%201.40%20crore%20on%20Sunday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722837328000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112279520%2Cimgsize-80410.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fbad-newz-box-office-collection-vicky-kaushal-starrer-earns-rs-1-40-crore-on-sunday%2Farticleshow%2F112279550.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112279550.cms%5C%22%20hspace