s%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358168%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Compiled%20by%20Padma%20Jyothi%20and%20Chitra%20Paul%2C%20'Talking%20Fingers'%20is%20a%20book%20written%20by%2032%20individuals%20with%20nonspeaking%20autism.%20The%20authors%20use%20this%20book%20to%20share%20their%20dreams%20and%20hopes%2C%20with%20just%20one%20request%20from%20the%20reader--%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20underestimate%20our%20capabilities.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A91%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358168%2Fpeople-with-nonspeaking-autism-in-india-talking-fingers-book-authors-padma-jyothi-chitra-paul%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20110%20km%20Long%20River%20Was%20Left%20To%20Die%2C%20Until%20an%20IAS%20Officer%20Helped%20Revive%20It%20in%206%20Months%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERoughly%2050%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Sot%20river%20%E2%80%93%20a%20tributary%20of%20the%20mighty%20Ganges%20%E2%80%93%20was%20a%20lifeline%20for%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20Sambhal%20district%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20farmers%20depending%20on%20its%20water%20for%20irrigating%20their%20lush%20green%20paddy%20and%20peppermint%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20river%20that%20passes%20through%2071%20%3Cem%3Egram%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20five%20development%20blocks%20disappeared%20from%20the%20district%20due%20to%20large-scale%20encroachment%20and%20neglect.%20In%202022%2C%20when%20the%20newly-appointed%20district%20magistrate%20IAS%20Manish%20Bansal%20visited%20the%20field%2C%20he%20found%20there%20was%20hardly%20any%20water%20in%20the%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20that%20the%20river%20was%20practically%20non-existent.%20We%20could%20only%20see%20small%20%3Cem%3Epuliya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(culverts)%20that%20were%20once%20made%20over%20the%20river.%20At%20several%20points%2C%20farmers%20had%20started%20growing%20crops%20considering%20it%20to%20be%20vacant%20land.%20The%20streak%20of%20the%20river%20was%20not%20completely%20connected%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20some%20places%2C%20the%20area%20was%20covered%20in%20small%20puddles.%20The%20river%20was%20encroached%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20it%20lost%20its%20path%20of%20natural%20flow%20downstream.%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20nearby%20areas%20would%20remain%20waterlogged%20during%20monsoon.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20Sot%20river%20acted%20as%20a%20natural%20drainage%20system%20for%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%20groundwater%20table%20had%20drastically%20reduced%20in%20the%20area%20as%20farmers%20became%20dependent%20on%20borewells%2C%20which%20further%20exacerbated%20the%20water%20problem%20in%20the%20region.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20hand%20pumps%2C%20as%20deep%20as%2050%20feet%2C%20started%20becoming%20non-functional%20because%20of%20the%20receding%20water%20table%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-2-1722402541.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22When%20former%20district%20magistrate%20IAS%20Manish%20Bansal%20visited%20the%20field%2C%20he%20found%20there%20was%20hardly%20any%20water%20in%20the%20river.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-2-1722402541.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-2-1722402541-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-2-1722402541-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-2-1722402541-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-2-1722402541-150x79.j