%20encroachments%20on%20the%20river%20area%20which%20had%20become%20flat%20at%20some%20points.%20Although%20there%20was%20no%20permanent%20construction%2C%20people%20started%20using%20it%20to%20grow%20crops.%20As%20it%20was%20illegal%20usage%2C%20we%20sought%20the%20help%20of%20the%20revenue%20land%20records%20team%20to%20clear%20encroachments%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%20step%20was%20desilting%20of%20the%20river%20to%20remove%20fine%20silt%20and%20sediment%20collected%20in%20the%20river%20and%20restore%20it%20to%20its%20natural%20capacity.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20roped%20in%20MGNREGA%20(Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act)%20workers%20to%20clean%20and%20dig%20the%20riverbed%20afresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%20December%202022%2C%20the%20project%20was%20completed%20in%20six%20months%20by%20June%202023.%20During%20the%20last%20monsoon%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348157%2Fmanganga-river-solapur-rejuvenation-efforts-vaijinath-ghongade-awarded-book-parikrama-mangangechi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20river%20captured%20the%20rainwater%20and%20was%20revived%20to%20its%20old%20glory%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20region%20was%20also%20free%20from%20waterlogging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-1-1722402513.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20district%20administration%20roped%20in%20MGNREGA%20workers%20to%20clean%20and%20dig%20the%20riverbed%20afresh.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-1-1722402513.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-1-1722402513-300x157.j